languages.text: "Кто же пьет воду на празднике, болван? Амасека мне, живо!"
"Who drinks water at a feast, you dimwit? Hurry up and bring me some amasec!"

languages.text: 「宴で水なんか飲む奴がいるかよ、このまぬけ！さっさとアマセックを持ってこい！」
languages.original_text: "Who drinks water at a feast, you dimwit? Hurry up and bring me some amasec!"

languages.text: "Ziyafette su içildiğini gördün mü hiç budala? Çabuk, bana amasek getir!"
languages.original_text: "Who drinks water at a feast, you dimwit? Hurry up and bring me some amasec!"

traits.locale_text: "Ziyafette su içildiğini gördün mü hiç seni budala? Çabuk, bana biraz amasek getir!"

languages.text: «¿Quién bebe agua en un banquete, necio? ¡Corre a traerme amasec!».
languages.original_text: "Who drinks water at a feast, you dimwit? Hurry up and bring me some amasec!"

traits.locale_text: «¿Quién bebe agua en un banquete, necio? ¡Corre a traerme amasec!».

languages.text: “你这个蠢货！哪有人在宴会上喝水的啊？快给我弄点艾玛赛克酒来！”
languages.original_text: "Who drinks water at a feast, you dimwit? Hurry up and bring me some amasec!"

traits.locale_text: “你这个蠢货！哪有人在宴会上喝水的啊？快给我弄点艾玛赛克酒来！”

languages.text: « Peuh ! A-t-on jamais vu qui que ce soit boire de l'eau à un banquet, imbécile ? Apporte-moi plutôt de l'amasec, et plus vite que ça ! »
languages.original_text: "Who drinks water at a feast, you dimwit? Hurry up and bring me some amasec!"

languages.text: "Wer trinkt Wasser bei einem Fest, du Einfaltspinsel? Mach hin und bring mir Amasec!"
